nd preparing to compete at the seventh Games of his career following his debut atSydneyin 2000.\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Shire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2072646396795004e-18, \"text\": \"Bywater\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Shire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Shire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a four-time bronze medallist\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"the seventh Games\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"his debut\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"atSydneyin\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony of Paris' maiden Paralympic Games takes place on Wednesday evening.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.0257321792068614e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday evening\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Up to 4,400 athletes are due to parade along the Champs-Elysees to Place de Concorde in front of an estimated 65,000 spectators.\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1183, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.955517251597007, \"rank\": 0.04655346753148815, \"text\": \"Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Up to 4,400 athletes\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"parade\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"the Champs-Elysees\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"an estimated 65,000 spectators\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competition starts on Thursday, with medals up for grabs in track cycling, swimming, taekwondo and table tennis, and continues until the closing ceremony on Sunday, September 8.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competition\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"grabs\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"track cycling\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"taekwondo\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"table tennis\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following Whiley's retirement, Shuker will partner 21-year-old Games newcomer Abbie Breakwell in the French capital - beginning on Friday at Roland Garros - and will also enter the women's singles draw.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Whiley's retirement\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"Shuker\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"21-year-old Games newcomer Abbie Breakwell\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"the French capital\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"Roland Garros\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's singles\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 44-ye